  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BIMParser.BadRecordFormatListener
    A listener for handling problems due to bad record formatting.

    A listener for handling problems due to bad record formatting.
    PEDParser.RecordListener
    A listener for handling parsed sample records and problems due to bad record formatting.

    A sample record.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BIMParser
    A parser for the PLINK extended MAP input file format described at http://pngu.mgh.harvard.edu/~purcell/plink/data.shtml#bed.
    MAPParser
    A parser for the PLINK MAP input file format described in the basic usage/data formats section of the online documentation.
    MAPWriter
    A writer for the PLINK MAP input file format described in the basic usage/data formats section of the online documentation.
    PEDParser
    A parser for the PLINK PED input file format described in the basic usage/data formats section of the online documentation.
    PEDWriter
    A writer for the PLINK PED input file format described in the basic usage/data formats section of the online documentation.
